review.reviewBody: Love the Spaghetti Pomodoro (Vegetarian), for pasta night.  Good tomato flavour with the right amount of heat. Portion size was quite generous too. Crispy Mashed Potato is a regular hit here too. Add the apple pie for a delicious finish.
Fantastic experience tonight. Ordered Herb Crush Salmon, Crispy Mashed Potato and Individually Baked Apple Pie - Maple. Every item was thoughtfully packed, fresh, and very flavourful.

Individually Baked Apple Pie - Vanilla is delicious! It's by far the best individual Apple pie in town. The pie crust and nuts have a nice crisp/crunch.  The vanilla ice cream is the perfect pairing, the ice cream is light.

Spaghetti Pomodoro (Vegetarian) & Individually Baked Apple Pie - Maple was delicious!😋 It was well packed so things stayed warm & dessert stayed cold. Presentation was great too. Definitely recommend this place. Food is yummy!👍😋

Herb Crush Salmon from here is better than fish from earls, cactus and flying pig. Refreshingly large portion, not overcooked/dry, had tasty greens and was very well seasoned. 
Hope they can keep up the quality, I will order again.
